subs.text: I have a really bad cold, or something. I'll start writing again when I feel better. For now I'm sleeping, hydrating and binge-watching. Just watched season 2 of Fleabag. Not sure what's next.

At what point will cities license their name to companies. So San Francisco changes to Salesforce. "I'm catching a flight from JFK to Salesforce, honey." You can imagine the rest. The United States is already spoken for.
